%a %b %e %H:%M:%S %Z %Y
.sp
.RE
in the C or POSIX locale, resulting in an output like
.RS
.sp
Wed Feb 26 17:48:54 CET 2003
.sp
.RE
.SH "ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES"
.TP
.B "LANG, LC_ALL"
